---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Land O'Frost — Customer Story — Formic"
  description="Land O'Frost replaced manual palletizing of 128,000 lbs/day with 5 gantry palletizers in 2 weekends, cutting OpEx by 20%."
  ogTitle="Land O'Frost — Formic Customer Story"
  ogDescription="5 gantry palletizers · 2 weekends · 20% OpEx reduction"
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/stories/land-o-frost" slot="head" />

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/stories">Customer Stories</a><span class="sep">/</span>Land O'Frost
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">Customer Story · Land O'Frost</div>
    <h1>128,000 lbs/day,<br><em>palletized.</em></h1>
    <p class="lede">Five gantry palletizers, deployed across two weekends, replaced the most physically punishing job on Land O'Frost's floor — and pulled 20% out of OpEx in the process.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <video autoplay muted loop playsinline poster="/Haviland_Products_-_Palletizing_poster.jpg">
        <source src="/RFA_header.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
      <span class="dv-fpo">FPO</span>
      <span class="dv-cap">Land O'Frost · gantry palletizing</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">01 — The Challenge</div>
      <h2>The hardest job <em>on the floor</em>.</h2>
      <p>Land O'Frost was running 128,000 lbs of product per day across its packing lines, and palletizing was the bottleneck. Manual stacking made changeovers slow, exhausted operators by the end of every shift, and exposed the line to lift-related injuries.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>128,000 lbs/day of finished product</li>
        <li>Highest-injury task on the floor</li>
        <li>Slow SKU changeover dragging on throughput</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Haviland_Products_-_Palletizing.gif" alt="Gantry palletizer at Land O'Frost" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Gantry palletizing · 24/7</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Talos-0095.jpg" alt="Land O'Frost end-of-line cell" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Pack · seal · palletize</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">02 — The Solution</div>
      <h2>Five palletizers, <em>two weekends</em>.</h2>
      <p>Formic deployed five gantry palletizers across Land O'Frost's existing lines in two weekends — no major plant retrofit, no shutdowns. Each cell integrated directly with the upstream packers and downstream wrap, under one Full Service agreement.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>5 gantry palletizers, deployed in 2 weekends</li>
        <li>Direct integration with existing packers and conveyors</li>
        <li>Single Full Service agreement covering all 5 cells</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px;text-align:center">
    <div class="db-tag" style="justify-content:center">03 — The Outcome</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(40px,5vw,72px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1;color:var(--white);margin:18px 0 56px">20% OpEx reduction. <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">Zero lift injuries.</em></h2>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1)">
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">5</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Gantry palletizers</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">2</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">Weekends to deploy</div></div>
      <div style="background:var(--black);padding:36px 24px"><div style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:48px;font-weight:500;color:var(--orange);line-height:1">20%</div><div style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(240,245,241,.55);margin-top:12px">OpEx reduction</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Ready to scope <em>your line?</em></h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="mailto:sales@formic.co" class="btn-ctadark">Get Started</a>
    <a href="/stories" class="btn-ctawh">More Customer Stories</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
